    "content" : "Got the rear chassis section removed: \n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1859774.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1859775.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Started stripping the old chassis rails and handbrake tubes etc off:\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1859773.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1859772.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Ready to go to the dippers. Gonna have a few repairs to do though... Was hoping this section was going to be better than it is, oh well:\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1860387.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1860388.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Should get back on it the end of the week \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Grin\">",
    "lastEdited" : "Tue Jan 08, 2019 8:55 pm"
  }, {
    "postId" : "919173",
    "author" : {
