    },
    "content" : "Moved onto removing the front section of chassis.\n<br> \n<br> Got the doglegs, tubs and cab floor out. They needed replacing and were in the way. Bulkhead needs a bit of work too:\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1867542.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1867541.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Then got the front chassis section out:\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1867546.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1867547.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1867548.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Need to get this cleaned up and off to be blasted ready to fit to the new chassis rails.\n<br> \n<br> \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Grin\">",
