    "postId" : "919297",
    "author" : {
      "username" : "mabbo",
      "userId" : "919297",
      "joined" : "Wed Jun 01, 2011 7:09 pm",
      "profileRank" : "SSVC Member",
      "location" : "Wolverhampton",
      "postCount" : "80",
      "avatarPath" : null
    },
    "content" : "<blockquote>\n <div>\n  <cite><a href=\"./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=124&amp;sid=0440d3c7278782de78be1841c1e83ab8\">vwJim</a> wrote: <a href=\"./viewtopic.php?p=919178&amp;sid=0440d3c7278782de78be1841c1e83ab8#p919178\" data-post-id=\"919178\" onclick=\"if(document.getElementById(hash.substr(1)))href=hash\">↑</a>\n   <div class=\"responsive-hide\">\n    Fri Jan 25, 2019 8:28 am\n   </div></cite> Great to see another resto place taking the effort to build a chassis jig. \n </div>\n</blockquote> I was originally looking for a Celette or car-o-liner or similar. I missed out on one, and all the others I found were complete with the dozer that Im not too fussed about, and they were all really expensive... Building my own took ages but Im pretty pleased with it. All the brackets are removable so I can use it on Bays and Beetles too when I get around to making more brackets \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Grin\">",
    "lastEdited" : "Tue Jan 29, 2019 3:41 pm"
  }, {
    "postId" : "919298",
    "author" : {
      "username" : "mabbo",
      "userId" : "919298",
      "joined" : "Wed Jun 01, 2011 7:09 pm",
      "profileRank" : "SSVC Member",
      "location" : "Wolverhampton",
      "postCount" : "80",
      "avatarPath" : null
    },
    "content" : "<blockquote>\n <div>\n  <cite><a href=\"./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=35667&amp;sid=0440d3c7278782de78be1841c1e83ab8\">markp</a> wrote: <a href=\"./viewtopic.php?p=919208&amp;sid=0440d3c7278782de78be1841c1e83ab8#p919208\" data-post-id=\"919208\" onclick=\"if(document.getElementById(hash.substr(1)))href=hash\">↑</a>\n   <div class=\"responsive-hide\">\n    Fri Jan 25, 2019 10:55 pm\n   </div></cite> I think you'll find few people who would be happy to rent that job once you have finished with it \n  <br> \n  <br> \n  <br> Looks fab ..... good luck and ENJOY !!!!!!\n  <br> \n  <br> \n  <br> Mark \n </div>\n</blockquote> Cheers Mark. Looks like your making good progress on your Beetle \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Grin\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<br> I got all the original parts that will be reused from the chassis ready for blasting.\n<br> \n<br> Rear parts:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869082.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Front parts:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869083.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> The floor section was better than I thought it would be, hopefully its just a small repair at the back corner needed:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869084.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> The beam mount sections are going to need some work though:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869085.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869087.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869088.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869089.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Got the seat runner and the extra section thats fitted to the cab tool chest area off and it seems to fit the new BBT panel pretty nice:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1869081.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Could do with finding a pair of rear bump stop brackets if anyone has any? \n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1860385.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Cant wait to get the new chassis together \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":D\" title=\"Big Grin\">",
    "lastEdited" : "Tue Jan 29, 2019 3:43 pm"
  }, {
