    "content" : "Had the chassis parts blasted:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879316.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Not as nice as I had hoped. Rotten in quite a few places:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879320.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879319.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879317.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Rest of the parts:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879315.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879314.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> I repaired the rotten corner of the front floor section:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879321.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879322.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879323.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879324.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Trial assembly of new chassis and front section:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879331.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879332.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879333.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Found a solid rear cut including the complete rear chassis rails so decided to use the whole rear end as the pressings were nicer than the repro chassis rails around where the support bar is welded. New piece tacked in place temporary:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879334.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> The front inner chassis legs were flat and needed shaping to fit the bulge in the bulkhead:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879335.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/1879336.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Thats it for now \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Grin\">",
