    "content" : "Thanks Mark \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Grin\">\n<br> \n<br> Not got anything done on it the last couple of weeks Im afraid, been getting a customers 66 Beetle painted after we finished the metalwork:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/rn8pp7vn34aukt7/Photo%2007-03-2019%2C%2013%2041%2007.jpg?dl=0\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> After a flat and polish:\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/2hotpb2lk87y57u/Photo%2008-03-2019%2C%2017%2045%2051.jpg?dl=0\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/owp060iex3mznxc/Photo%2008-03-2019%2C%2017%2046%2028.jpg?dl=0\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/flcihzcshqhhsxy/Photo%2014-03-2019%2C%2015%2025%2022.jpg?dl=0\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<img src=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/8i48aor1nnp3tjs/Photo%2015-03-2019%2C%2015%2016%2056.jpg?dl=0\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Will be back on the crewcab before the end of the month though \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":D\" title=\"Big Grin\">",
